11#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event_log_factory.h"
12
13#include <memory>
14#include <utility>
15
16#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
17#include "system_wrappers/include/field_trial.h"
18
19#ifdef WEBRTC_ENABLE_RTC_EVENT_LOG
20#include "logging/rtc_event_log/rtc_event_log_impl.h"
21#endif
22
23namespace webrtc {
24
25RtcEventLogFactory::RtcEventLogFactory(TaskQueueFactory* task_queue_factory)
26 : task_queue_factory_(task_queue_factory) {
27 RTC_DCHECK(task_queue_factory_);
28}
29
30std::unique_ptr<RtcEventLog> RtcEventLogFactory::CreateRtcEventLog(
31 RtcEventLog::EncodingType encoding_type) {
32#ifdef WEBRTC_ENABLE_RTC_EVENT_LOG
33 if (field_trial::IsEnabled("WebRTC-RtcEventLogKillSwitch")) {
34 return std::make_unique<RtcEventLogNull>();
35 }
36 return std::make_unique<RtcEventLogImpl>(encoding_type, task_queue_factory_);
37#else
38 return std::make_unique<RtcEventLogNull>();
39#endif
40}
41
42} // namespace webrtc
